                                MetaRover is a Google Sheets <a href="https://developers.google.com/apps-script/add-ons/" target="_blank">Add-on</a> which can parse URLs from XML sitemaps and scrape html tags and their content in <a href="https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/url-fetch/http-response#getContentText()" target="_blank">text format</a> from a list of URLs utilizing Google Apps Script's <a href="https://developers.google.com/apps-script/reference/url-fetch/url-fetch-app" target="_blank">URLFetchApp service</a>.
